        "can_wiki": false,
        "cooked": "<p>PARAMETRIC MODEL MAKER feature request:</p>\n<p>As we now have the ability to upload files in a somewhat limited capacity (PNG, SVG, STL) I want to suggest adding the ability to upload custom font files (.TTF, .OTF).</p>\n<p>Openscad has a fairly robust text feature set, and being able to use custom fonts would really, really open up the possibilities here.</p>",
