        "cooked": "<p>But a Slicer isn\u2019t a CAD program. So this is a specious comparison.</p>\n<p>You can probably use any font you want in any CAD program you use. I do. If you don\u2019t know how to use CAD software, it\u2019s something worth learning so that you aren\u2019t constrained by the limitations of the slicer\u2026</p>",
